0.3.0:
-------

logged in administrators can bypass Store Maintenance if activated
custom maintenance page can be defined for each store
added comments to backend configuration


0.2.0:
-------

Define a list of IP addresses which are allowed to access the frontend.
Other ip addresses are blocked.
All access attempts are logged to special log file
Log file can be defined in backend
Log verbosity can be defined in backend
Logging can be switched off
 

More features coming soon ...
